# LangGraph Enterprise Mastery Curriculum Plan

This plan establishes a high-density mastery repository incorporating practical codebase translations (`langgraph_mastery/`) alongside deep theoretical syllabus explanations (`langgraph_topics/`) mirroring the official LangChain/LangGraph curriculum.

